message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a method for coronary artery centerline extraction using a convolutional neural network (CNN) and cardiac CT angiography (CCTA) images. This involves image analysis and machine learning, which are relevant to computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the method is in medical imaging, specifically in cardiac imaging (cs.MED). The use of a CNN also suggests a neural network approach (cs.NEURON).
